  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> sleep two and are approximately 15m². All rooms have a bath or shower, WC, TV, safe and hair dryer. This room can be requested for sole use at a supplement. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Triple Room </strong>sleep up to four people with either a single or double sofa bed. For four guests, room must be requested. </p>
<p>Some rooms in the hotel come with a balcony but cannot be guaranteed.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
